{"tid":2112441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★寰宇殯儀館有確診者到場拜祭","createTime":"2020-07-17T10:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T10:31:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4693da1000f70e23cec12e18a1f4b0dd8f60d067","tid":2112441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紅磡寰宇殯儀館昨日（16日）有一名死者親友到殯儀館拜祭，惟同晚被告知確診新冠肺炎。館內貼出告示指館方已向衞生署通報情況，並指當晚已聘請消毒承辦商到館內進行全面消毒。殯儀館所屬的東華三院發言人表示，昨晚殯儀館值班的員工共有7人，院方會安排他們接受病毒檢測，由於殯儀館昨晚已進行全館消毒清潔，暫毋需休館。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/499327/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%AF%B0%E5%AE%87%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E9%A4%A8%E6%9C%89%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E6%8B%9C%E7%A5%AD-%E9%A4%A8%E6%96%B9-%E7%95%B6%E6%99%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F499327%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25AF%25B0%25E5%25AE%2587%25E6%25AE%25AF%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%25A5%25AD-%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2599%259A%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=42dc2c57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/499327/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%AF%B0%E5%AE%87%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E9%A4%A8%E6%9C%89%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E6%8B%9C%E7%A5%AD-%E9%A4%A8%E6%96%B9-%E7%95%B6%E6%99%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92</a>"},{"pid":"d56bd4977acf69afbdcbb51d5a4f9aba0108048b","tid":2112441,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"拜定自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d138c1e949b56a3bfe94574a23657335c0eaba7","tid":2112441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"確診者昨晚曾到訪殯儀館5樓一個靈堂拜祭，記者今午到寰宇殯儀館視察，館內貼出告示指一名新型冠狀病毒確診者昨晚到訪拜祭，館方已向衞生署通報情況，並指當晚已聘請消毒承辦商到館內進行全面消毒，告示又指進入館內人士需要佩戴外科口罩及量體溫，並表明不招待隔離及確診人士。殯儀館地下登記處外有戴上口罩職員為訪客登記，並設有紅外線測溫鏡頭及為訪客提供消毒搓手液。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">7值班員工將接受檢測 東華：暫無需休館<br />\n</span><br />\n東華三院發言人回覆指，昨晚當確診者得悉確診後，已即時離開殯儀館，而當晚儀式亦加快完成，主家並提早1小時離開，今日主家只進行簡單大殮儀式後便離開往火化場，殯儀館館於大殮後亦安排清潔公司再為靈堂消毒。發言人又指昨晚殯儀館值班的員工共有7人，院方會安排他們接受病毒檢測，由於殯儀館昨晚已進行全館消毒清潔，暫無需休館。<br />\n<br />\n寰宇殯儀館助理營運經理梁先生表示，事發當晚已有衞生署職員全副裝備到殯儀館進行消毒清潔，今早亦再有衞生署人員到場清潔。問到消息傳開後生意有沒有受到影響，梁先生表示由於報導於今早才刊登，生意暫時未有影響。"},{"pid":"20cfd83a2d441ba9be1ed0246819dfdfc5fc51f0","tid":2112441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4879895/org/0931ea800f2d5e876844255acbae12b7.jpg/CX5vz-qimdb1dASOhvNMwWBPaBsuiRP8MjCXyxgwl8s?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4879895%2Forg%2F0931ea800f2d5e876844255acbae12b7.jpg%2FCX5vz-qimdb1dASOhvNMwWBPaBsuiRP8MjCXyxgwl8s%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=e474e238&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b09d76d4e7574397ecbec2a1758577147938ea98","tid":2112441,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"今次破地獄都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580a1d2bc9031ba52066950a9f5564a6a03966f6","tid":2112441,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c094349d4c22ffc80fcfb3d3431e918c1d919d03","tid":2112441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09d76d4e7574397ecbec2a1758577147938ea98","tid":2112441,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"今次破地獄都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"地獄 爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1527bbb24284e8e96ff52593d55b04eca0f819d6","tid":2112441,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"奈何橋 發現有確診者，孟婆home office"},{"pid":"2a421963c73cd040ba20d2115147e66a62e4212a","tid":2112441,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"生意興隆"}]}